That being said, there's 2 major differences between that guy and manaburn.<br>
<br>
#1 - It's 3 different classes. Don't underestimate how much VI hated all the SAME class killing something. They'd much rather see 3 different classes than 3 wizards.<br>
<br>
#2 - It took him over an hour. Wizards burning took 6 seconds, 10 minutes to med and 6 seconds to do it over again. Big difference.<br>
<br>
